remarks_zh: 1 月 21 日起出現發燒及鼻塞，被發現發燒，即時被送往醫院
remarks_en: Developed fever and blocked nose since Jan 21; Was detected to have fever and was immediately taken to the hospital

remarks_zh: 由武漢到深圳北（三號車廂 10D 座位）
remarks_en: From Wuhan to Shenzhenbei (carriage no. 3, seat no. 10D)

remarks_zh: 由深圳北到香港（二號車廂 2D 座位）
remarks_en: From Shenzhenbei to Hong Kong (carriage no. 2, seat no. 2D)

remarks_zh: 患者與妻子、兩名兒子及外母同行，患者家屬入住尖沙咀皇悅酒店。
remarks_en: The patient travelled with his wife, two sons and his mother-in-law. The patient's relatives stayed at the Empire Hotel Kowloon.

remarks_zh: 患者的親屬離港前往馬尼拉
remarks_en: The patient's relatives departed Hong Kong for Manila.

remarks_zh: 獨自到武漢探望父母；1 月 18 日起發燒
remarks_en: Visited his parents; fever since Jan 18

remarks_zh: 由武漢到深圳
remarks_en: From Wuhan to Shenzhen

remarks_zh: 乘東鐵轉馬鐵返馬鞍山
remarks_en: Took the subway (on the East Rail Line and the Ma On Shan Line) to Ma On Shan

remarks_zh: 乘搭的士前往威爾斯親王醫院
remarks_en: To Prince of Wales Hospital by taxi

location_zh: 威爾斯親王醫院急症室
location_en: Prince of Wales Hospital Accident & Emergency Department

location_zh: 威爾斯親王醫院急症室

remarks_zh: 覆診；由於發燒持續，獲安排入院接受隔離治療
remarks_en: Follow-up; was admitted for hospital as his fever did not subside

remarks_zh: 患者與丈夫（第 #8 宗患者）來港探望女兒及女婿
remarks_en: Visited her daughter and son-in-law with her husband (patient no. 8)

remarks_zh: 由武漢到深圳北
remarks_en: From Wuhan to Shenzhenbei

remarks_zh: 由深圳北到香港
remarks_en: From Shenzhenbei to Hong Kong

remarks_zh: 1 月 20 日起出現發燒及咳嗽
remarks_en: Developed fever and cough since Jan 20

location_en: Tuen Mun Hospital Accident & Emergency Departments
Tuen Mun Hospital Accident & Emergency Departments
remarks_zh: 入院接受隔離
remarks_en: Was admitted for isolation

remarks_zh: 患者與丈夫（第 5 宗患者）同行
remarks_en: Travelled with her husband (patient no. 5)

remarks_zh: 1 月 23 日起開始發燒
remarks_en: Developed fever since Jan 23

remarks_zh: 患者與妻子（第 4 宗患者）同行
remarks_en: Travelled with his wife (patient no. 4)

remarks_zh: 1 月 23 日起開始咳嗽
remarks_en: Developed cough since Jan 23

location_zh: 威爾斯親王醫院急症室

remarks_zh: 1 月 20 日發燒，翌日到武漢一醫院求醫，同日退燒
remarks_en: Developed fever on Jan 20; sought treatment at a hospital in Wuhan the next day and his fever subsided

remarks_zh: 由咸寧到深圳北 （二號車廂第 11 行）
remarks_en: From Xianning to Shenzhenbei (carriage no.2, row no. 11)

remarks_en: Developed fever again on Jan 24

remarks_zh: 就 12 月尾在內地被狗咬傷求醫，當時並無發燒
remarks_en: Sought treatment for dog bite in the Mainland in late Dec; no fever at that moment
